| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5061 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9d006a87-76e9-51a4-a14b-bf1ac8550ce0"
